## How Wyatt works
- Directs Cursor via prompts, does not hand-edit code
- Commits frequently, reverts over debugging broken state
- Pushback > validation; start new agents if Cursor spirals on the same code
- Screenshots for visual review mid-session
- Production verification rule: post-push, fetch production main.js and grep for the new code. Local grep alone has produced false positives.

